17 C.(1) The court may authorize a curator to make a donation pursuant
18 to Subsection A of this Section when the procedure provided for in Code of Civil
19 Procedure Articles 4271 and 4566 is complied with and the donation does not
20 materially impair the financial condition of the interdict and is not likely to
